[2.798862, "o", "  \u001b[33mYour agent identity has been successfully registered on-chain with a stake of 0.01 ETH. The transaction hash is 2934a4117a5de7e9b027ff38bc7687a03319ba81a3c110481505df2118eb64c4 and it was recorded in block number 2. You now have a permanent, verifiable identity on the ERC-8004 chain with capabilities in inference and code_review.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[32mUser >\u001b[0m What does the Bittensor subnet look like right now?\r\n"]
[3.912807, "o", "  \u001b[2m[tool: settlement_subnet_info]\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m{\r\n  \"netuid\": 1,\r\n  \"network\": \"test\",\r\n  \"neurons\": 256,\r\n  \"block\": 7004390,\r\n  \"mock\": false\r\n}\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.37516, "o", "  \u001b[33mThe Bittensor subnet currently has the following characteristics: \u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[33m- Network ID: 1\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[33m- Environment: test\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[33m- Number of neurons: 256\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[33m- Current block: 7004390\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[33m- Real-world status: true (not a mock network)\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[32mUser >\u001b[0m I just completed a task successfully. Record it and show me my updated reputation.\r\n"]
