[5.568282, "o", "  \u001b[33mYour task completion has been recorded on-chain successfully with transaction hash ef0a9106efe614ce25c624cc52ca5fae7e69fa5b531b206341b5163771d7208e. \u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[33m\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[33mYour updated reputation scores are as follows:\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[33m- On ERC-8004 chain: 1.0 (based on 1 completed task)\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[33m- On Bittensor subnet: 0.0 (no completed tasks yet, but the score will update with more data)\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[32mUser >\u001b[0m Check all my balances — ETH and TAO.\r\n"]
