[6.393369, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[36m======================================================================\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[36m  Demo Complete\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[36m======================================================================\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  Hermes (hermes3:8b) called settlement tools natively\r\n  through its own tool registry — no wrapper, no adapter.\r\n  The same tools appear in `hermes tools` alongside\r\n  the 40+ built-in tools.\r\n\r\n"]
